text:
The hour's now come;
[p]The very minute bids thee ope thine ear;
[p]Obey and be attentive. Canst thou remember
[p]A time before we came unto this cell?
[p]I do not think thou canst, for then thou wast not
[p]Out three years old.

Pardon, master;
[p]I will be correspondent to command
[p]And do my spiriting gently.

Shake it off. Come on;
[p]We'll visit Caliban my slave, who never
[p]Yields us kind answer.

No;
[p]I will resist such entertainment till
[p]Mine enemy has more power.

I' the commonwealth I would by contraries
[p]Execute all things; for no kind of traffic
[p]Would I admit; no name of magistrate;
[p]Letters should not be known; riches, poverty,
[p]And use of service, none; contract, succession,
[p]Bourn, bound of land, tilth, vineyard, none;
[p]No use of metal, corn, or wine, or oil;
[p]No occupation; all men idle, all;
[p]And women too, but innocent and pure;
[p]No sovereignty;--

Draw together;
[p]And when I rear my hand, do you the like,
[p]To fall it on Gonzalo.

I prithee, let me bring thee where crabs grow;
[p]And I with my long nails will dig thee pignuts;
[p]Show thee a jay's nest and instruct thee how
[p]To snare the nimble marmoset; I'll bring thee
[p]To clustering filberts and sometimes I'll get thee
[p]Young scamels from the rock. Wilt thou go with me?

If you'll sit down,
[p]I'll bear your logs the while: pray, give me that;
[p]I'll carry it to the pile.

I warrant you sir;
[p]The white cold virgin snow upon my heart
[p]Abates the ardour of my liver.

A contract of true love to celebrate;
[p]And some donation freely to estate
[p]On the blest lovers.
